<section class="jury2">

    <div class="container">

        <div class="jury2__heading">

            <span class="jury2__subtitle">
                Juri Internasional
            </span>

            <h3 class="jury2__title">

                Temui Para Ahli

                <span class="jury2__title-secondary">
                    Di Balik Kompetisi
                </span>

            </h3>

            <p class="jury2__description">
                Panel internasional yang terdiri dari desainer, akademisi, produsen, dan profesional industri akan menilai setiap karya berdasarkan kreativitas, kelayakan produksi, potensi pasar, serta relevansi budaya.
            </p>

        </div>

        <div class="jury2__list">

            <!-- juri memmber 1 -->
            <article class="jury-member">

                <div class="jury-member__image">

                    <img
                        src="/juri_photo_junaidy.png"
                        alt="International Jury Member"
                        class="jury-member__image-item"
                    >

                </div>

                <div class="jury-member__content">

                    <h4 class="jury-member__name">
                        Deny Willy Junaidy
                    </h4>

                    <p class="jury-member__role">
                        Interior Design Researcher & Lecturer
                    </p>

                    <span class="jury-member__company">
                        Institut Teknologi Bandung • Indonesia
                    </span>

                    <p class="jury-member__text">
                        Deny Willy Junaidy adalah dosen dan peneliti di Fakultas Seni Rupa dan Desain ITB. Penelitiannya berfokus pada desain furnitur, desain interior, design cognition, serta pengembangan industri furnitur dan kerajinan berbasis budaya Indonesia. Ia juga memimpin Furniture & Living Design Lab di ITB.
                    </p>

                    <div class="jury-member__socials jury-member__socials-member1">

                        <a href="https://itb.ac.id/staf/profil/deny-willy-junaidy" target="_blank" aria-label="Website">
                            <img src="/website_icon.png" alt="">
                        </a>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </article>

            <!-- juri memmber 2 -->
            <article class="jury-member">

                <div class="jury-member__image">

                    <img
                        src="/juri_photo_19buro.jpg"
                        alt="International Jury Member"
                        class="jury-member__image-item"
                    >

                </div>

                <div class="jury-member__content">

                    <h4 class="jury-member__name">
                        Slava Nozdrachova
                    </h4>

                    <p class="jury-member__role">
                        Founder of 19BŪRO, Architecture & Interior Design Studio
                    </p>

                    <span class="jury-member__company">
                        19BŪRO
                    </span>

                    <blockquote class="jury-member__quote">
                        “Bagi saya, arsitektur adalah proses batin yang diwujudkan melalui material. Bukan menambahkan, melainkan menghilangkan. Bukan mengisi, melainkan membebaskan. Dari situlah lahir ruang tempat esensi dapat benar-benar terdengar.”
                    </blockquote>

                    <div class="jury-member__socials">

                        <a href="https://19buro.com/" target="_blank" aria-label="Website">
                            <img src="/website_icon.png" alt="">
                        </a>

                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/19.buro/" target="_blank" aria-label="Instagram">
                            <img src="/instagram_icon.png" alt="">
                        </a>

                        <a href="https://www.behance.net/19buro" target="_blank" aria-label="Behance">
                            <img src="/behance_icon.png" alt="">
                        </a>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </article>

            <!-- juri memmber 3 -->
            <article class="jury-member">

                <div class="jury-member__image">

                    <img
                        src="/juri_photo_minaev.JPG"
                        alt="International Jury Member"
                        class="jury-member__image-item jury-member__image-item--minaev"
                    >

                </div>

                <div class="jury-member__content">

                    <h4 class="jury-member__name">
                        Roman Minaev
                    </h4>

                    <p class="jury-member__role">
                        Founder & CEO of Woodara
                    </p>

                    <span class="jury-member__company">
                        Woodara
                    </span>

                    <p class="jury-member__text">
                        Pengusaha dan pendiri Woodara yang berfokus pada pengembangan furnitur Indonesia untuk pasar internasional. Ia bekerja sama dengan desainer dan produsen untuk menciptakan produk yang menggabungkan identitas lokal, kualitas tinggi, dan potensi komersial global.
                    </p>

                    <div class="jury-member__socials">

                        <a href="https://www.woodara.online/" target="_blank" aria-label="Website">
                            <img src="/website_icon.png" alt="">
                        </a>

                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/woodara.shop/" target="_blank" aria-label="Instagram">
                            <img src="/instagram_icon.png" alt="">
                        </a>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </article>

            <!-- juri memmber 4 -->
            <article class="jury-member">

                <div class="jury-member__image">

                    <img
                        src="/juri_photo_pinto.webp"
                        alt="International Jury Member"
                        class="jury-member__image-item"
                    >

                </div>

                <div class="jury-member__content">

                    <h4 class="jury-member__name">
                        Pinto
                    </h4>

                    <p class="jury-member__role">
                        Luxury Interior Design & Furniture House
                    </p>

                    <span class="jury-member__company">
                        PINTO • FRANCE
                    </span>

                    <p class="jury-member__text">
                        French design house renowned for creating exceptional interiors, bespoke furniture, and collectible design pieces. For decades, PINTO has delivered projects for private residences, hotels, yachts, and international luxury clients, combining craftsmanship, rare materials, and timeless elegance.
                    </p>

                    <div class="jury-member__socials">

                        <a href="https://www.pinto.fr/" target="_blank" aria-label="Website">
                            <img src="/website_icon.png" alt="">
                        </a>

                        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Pinto.Editions/?locale=fr_CA" target="_blank" aria-label="Facebook">
                            <img src="/facebook_icon.png" alt="">
                        </a>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </article>

        </div>

        <p class="jury-members__note">
            All communication with jury members is conducted exclusively through official Woodara channels.
        </p>

    </div>

</section>

<style>

    .jury2 {
        background-color: #111;
        padding: 8rem 0;
    }

    .jury2 .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 140rem;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* heading */
    .jury2__heading {
        max-width: 66rem;
        margin-bottom: 8rem;
    }

    .jury2__subtitle {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        color: #fff; 
        font-size: 1.2rem; 
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 3.2rem;
    }

    .jury2__subtitle::before {
        content: ""; 
        display: inline-block;
        width: 0.6rem; 
        height: 0.6rem; 
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 50%; 
        margin-right: 1rem;
    }

    .jury2__title {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: clamp(4.2rem, 5vw, 5.4rem);
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1.12;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .jury2__title-secondary {
        font-style: italic;
        color: #888;
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    .jury2__description {
        max-width: 66rem;
        color: #888;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* members */

    .jury2__list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 6rem;
    }

    .jury-member {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 25rem 1fr;
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: start;
    }

    .jury-member__image {
        width: 25rem;
        aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .jury-member__image-item {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        display: block;
    }

    .jury-member__image-item--minaev {
        object-position: center 10%;
    }

    .jury-member__content {
        max-width: 90rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .jury-member__name {
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .jury-member__role {
        color: #888;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 2.4rem;
    }

    .jury-member__company {
        display: inline-block;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.24rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 2.8rem;
    }

    .jury-member__text {
        color: #888;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .jury-member__quote {
        color: #888;
        line-height: 1.7;
        font-style: normal;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    .jury-members__note {
        margin-top: 6rem;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .jury-member__socials {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.2rem;
        margin-top: auto;
    }

    .jury-member__socials a {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        transition: .3s ease;
    }

    .jury-member__socials a:hover {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .jury-member__socials img {
        width: 3rem;
        height: 3rem;
    }

    /* mobile */

@media (max-width: 768px) {

    .jury2 {
        padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .jury2__heading {
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .jury2__subtitle {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .jury2__title {
        font-size: 3.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .jury2__description {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .jury2__list {
        gap: 5rem;
    }

    .jury-member {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
    }

    .jury-member__image {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 18rem;
    }

    .jury-member__name {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
    }

    .jury-member__role {
        margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    }

    .jury-member__company {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .jury-members__note {
        margin-top: 5rem;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .jury-member__socials {
        margin-top: 2.4rem;
    }
}

</style>